description:
Nikki considers changing her name to Nikki th6 Goddess. Not really. She's back in Los Angeles while Andrew is in studio touching the stuffed animals in indecent ways. Nikki does care about what Sidney Sweeney has to to say about the unglamorous and expensive side of Hollywood. They play the Esther Perel game Where Should We Begin? and tell stories about hurting someone unintentionally.
